ing: 3 frozen bananas, cut into small chunks
1/4 cup white sugar, or to taste
2 tablespoons whipped dairy topping, or to taste
des: "This is my 13-year-old son's creation. It's perfect on a hot summer day or as an after school treat."
ins: Put ice in a blender; add bananas, milk, sugar, strawberries, and vanilla extract. Blend until smooth. Top with whipped topping; blend again until smooth.
